{"tid":2316302,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"離岸證卷戶口　教學　免除離岸戶口很多限制　窮人亦可開戶","createTime":"2020-12-07T19:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-08T13:11:58.000Z","uid":261647,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8ca8bdb8db8d404ffcb8af98f5ff616e26a9fb7a","tid":2316302,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.921804054525995/3771145096258529/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.921804054525995%2F3771145096258529%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=1488e073\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FrontlineTechWorkersConcernGroup/photos/a.921804054525995/3771145096258529/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n作者：前線科技人員<br />\n<br />\n＃非廣告 香港政治環境不穩，唔少人都有諗過開離岸戶口做資產配置，但開離岸銀行戶口嘅門檻比較高而且限制比較多。<br />\n<br />\n其實有更簡單嘅方法，就係開離岸「證券」戶口。以 Firstrade 為例，所有手續可以喺網上完成，開戶一般可即日搞掂，完成後即可以電匯由本地銀行即時過數，錢一到戶就受美帝 SIPC 保護，由呢刻開始就唔駛怕俾身處逃犯天堂嘅壞人扣起你嘅錢，安全穩妥。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅朋友可以參考以下呢篇開戶教學 <img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/1/16/1f447.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft4f%2F1%2F16%2F1f447.png&h=58adc882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/1/16/1f447.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft4f%2F1%2F16%2F1f447.png&h=58adc882&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://static.xx.fbcdn.net/images/emoji.php/v9/t4f/1/16/1f447.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fimages%2Femoji.php%2Fv9%2Ft4f%2F1%2F16%2F1f447.png&h=58adc882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/Firstrade-open-account/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planto.hk%2Fzh%2Fblog%2FFirstrade-open-account%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=be3b0ff4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/Firstrade-open-account/</a><br />\n<br />\n*留意，另一間比較多人用嘅美國券商 Interactive Broker (IB) 喺香港開嘅美股戶口並 ＃不是 離岸戶口，有事美帝都幫唔到你<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yYnXWDz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyYnXWDz.jpg&h=79a00451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/Firstrade-open-account/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.planto.hk%2Fzh%2Fblog%2FFirstrade-open-account%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=be3b0ff4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.planto.hk/zh/blog/Firstrade-open-account/</a><br />\n<br />\n自去年以來，不少對香港前景感不安的人，透過開設離岸戶口（offshore account），將部分資產轉移海外，以分散地緣政治風險。證券戶口方面，以零佣金收費為賣點的第一證券（Firstrade）是其中一個可供香港用戶輕易申請的離岸戶口，頗受本地小散戶歡迎。<br />\n<br />\n而即使無意「走資」，用Firstrade投資美股亦具優勢，今次Planto為大家介紹它的優點、缺點、開戶流程，以及入錢和拎錢方式。 （ <a href=\"https://www.firstrade.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.firstrade.com%2F&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7DcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=7a678d66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.firstrade.com/</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n第一證券 Firstrade的優點及缺點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8srt3kC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8srt3kC.png&h=cbf82b58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一證券 Firstrade 開戶流程<br />\n<br />\n申請Firstrade賬戶的手續非常簡單，數分鐘即可完成：<br />\n<br />\n1. 經Firstrade網站開戶<br />\n2. 上載身份證明文件（香港人可用特區護照或BNO開戶）<br />\n3. 填寫基本資料如姓名、地址、電郵、就業狀況、投資偏好等<br />\n4. 設定電子簽名及遞交申請<br />\n<br />\n填妥資料後，用戶馬上會收到確認電郵。Planto團隊測試開戶時，在收到確認電郵後約5小時便順利開通賬戶，審批速度跟申請香港的美股證券戶口相差無幾。<br />\n<br />\n開戶後，即可入金及開始投資。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cms.planto.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firstrade開戶流程.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.planto.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFirstrade%E9%96%8B%E6%88%B6%E6%B5%81%E7%A8%8B.jpg&h=faa6e49a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n申請Firstrade賬戶過程只需數分鐘，一般可在一天內獲批。<br />\n<br />\n電匯存取資金　收費因銀行而異<br />\n<br />\n入金到Firstrade的方式跟其他證券戶口大同小異，只不過是透過國際匯款去完成。在銀行櫃枱或網上銀行賬戶提供收款銀行、美元金額、SWIFT碼、收款人資料（名稱賬戶），並注明用戶的賬戶號碼及英文全名即可。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cms.planto.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Firstrade.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.planto.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F04%2FFirstrade.jpg&h=d730c68f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nFirstrade收費便宜，但用戶須承擔匯款費用，匯率及匯款手續費因銀行而異。<br />\n<br />\n提取資金方面，我們向Firstrade查詢過，獲回覆指該公司不會向經銀行匯款拎錢的香港用戶收取手續費，但銀行通常收取約35美元費用，實際費用或因銀行而異。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cms.planto.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Firstrade-reply-planto-1024x257.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcms.planto.io%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F05%2FFirstrade-reply-planto-1024x257.jpg&h=7b9e5f52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我們以客戶身份向Firstrade查詢國際匯款收費，上圖是Firstrade的電郵回覆截圖。<br />\n<br />\n如使用Debit Card提款，一般收費是提款額3%；如賬戶資產達10,000美元以上者，每月可享一次上限1,000美元的免費提款。用戶宜避免頻繁提取資金，以減省出金支出。<br />\n<br />\n投資涉及風險，資訊僅作教學用途，並不構成投資意見或建議，故不應被視為作任何投資決定或行動的基礎。"},{"pid":"b7f83c5740b942efaad6a873d8d24e8e7d9db6ed","tid":2316302,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T19:39:01.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"a2ad767bf3dd1aac8c54dcc9b841ee6bfa18e2b2","tid":2316302,"uid":59753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T21:17:43.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"c6dc505ea3c06e2591f73042914bcfe2d973dd52","tid":2316302,"uid":138790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T21:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"536b2e08285cfabcd9066413c98c23ce561c4bbd","tid":2316302,"uid":30782,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T21:38:53.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51ed484a3f2561ab1e17f2b266a13a9ba9cc3f7","tid":2316302,"uid":118736,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T21:56:37.000Z","msg":"認真上年講到而家...<br />\n啲人仲係啱識醒既就算吧啦"},{"pid":"683a8ef3b119ee2ceb0c0d38c05b4085dd0ccdb5","tid":2316302,"uid":59955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:00:26.000Z","msg":"Firstrade 係咪冇香港版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會開錯唔係國際版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde48e58a0c3f5d65fefe860d1ac6fa10b193c54","tid":2316302,"uid":292227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:16:17.000Z","msg":"無知一問，開 firstrade係香港匯左錢入戶口，去到外國開完實體戶口後，要係 firstrade匯去外地實體得唔得？因淨係睇到教人開戶，睇過要轉其他開戶境外好似要再申請，怕到時離開香港唔知要點攪？<br />\n有無巴絲清楚講解下"},{"pid":"b054e77a8def0fb78f36359530a80ce5c89b9a3b","tid":2316302,"uid":380779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"開都開Charles Schwab International啦，點會用firstrade<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n規模、介面CS贏晒，firstrade仲要係華人背景"},{"pid":"8d890f329ff0dd363137fdb7cc4712b763ef1a23","tid":2316302,"uid":194298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cde48e58a0c3f5d65fefe860d1ac6fa10b193c54","tid":2316302,"uid":292227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:16:17.000Z","msg":"無知一問，開 firstrade係香港匯左錢入戶口，去到外國開完實體戶口後，要係 firstrade匯去外地實體得唔得？因淨係睇到教人開戶，睇過要轉其他開戶境外好似要再申請，怕到時離開香港唔知要點攪？<br />\n有無巴絲清楚講解下"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:48:39.000Z","msg":"外地對大額匯款好敏感，所以我都唔係好敢用香港-FT-外地咁走"},{"pid":"18a7d5fe1e9a5b4a8fdfc762e0dc03e3840a6281","tid":2316302,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b054e77a8def0fb78f36359530a80ce5c89b9a3b","tid":2316302,"uid":380779,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T22:47:43.000Z","msg":"開都開Charles Schwab Interna